{
  "cleaned_text": "# Platform Task-Center E2E Spec\n\nBase URL:\n\n- `http://127.0.0.1:8001`\n\nEnvironment:\n\n- `test`\n\nTarget system:\n\n- `http://127.0.0.1:8001`\n\nAll APIs use the same response envelope:\n\n{\n\"success\": true,\n\"code\": \"SOME_CODE\",\n\"message\": \"some message\",\n\"data\": {},\n\"timestamp\": \"2026-04-04T15:00:00+00:00\"\n}\n\n## Step 1\n\nRequest:\n\n- `POST /api/tasks`\n\nRequest body:\n\n{\n\"task_name\": \"platform_e2e_regression_demo\",\n\"source_type\": \"text\",\n\"requirement_text\": \"Validate the current platform task-center main flow.\",\n\"target_system\": \"http://127.0.0.1:8001\",\n\"environment\": \"test\"\n}\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `201`\n- `code = TASK_CREATED`\n- `data.task_id` exists\n- `data.task_context` exists\n- `data.task_context.task_id` exists\n- `data.task_context.task_name` exists\n\nSave context:\n\n- `task_id <- data.task_id`\n- `resource_id <- data.task_id`\n\n## Step 2\n\nRequest:\n\n- `GET /api/tasks/{task_id}`\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = TASK_DETAIL_OK`\n- `data.task_id = {task_id}`\n- `data.task_name` exists\n- `data.task_context` exists\n- `data.status` exists\n\n## Step 3\n\nRequest:\n\n- `POST /api/tasks/{task_id}/parse`\n\nRequest body:\n\n{\n\"use_llm\": false,\n\"rag_enabled\": true,\n\"retrieval_top_k\": 5,\n\"rerank_enabled\": false\n}\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = TASK_PARSED`\n- `data.task_id = {task_id}`\n- `data.parsed_requirement` exists\n- `data.parse_metadata` exists\n- `data.parse_metadata.parse_mode` exists\n- `data.parse_metadata.retrieval_mode` exists\n\n## Step 4\n\nRequest:\n\n- `GET /api/tasks/{task_id}/dsl`\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = DSL_OK`\n- `data.scenarios` exists\n- `data.scenarios` is not empty\n\nRequired generated request steps:\n\n- `POST /api/tasks`\n- `POST /api/tasks/{task_id}/parse`\n- `POST /api/tasks/{task_id}/execute`\n\nRequired create-step save_context:\n\n- `task_id = json.data.task_id`\n- `resource_id = json.data.task_id`\n\n## Step 5\n\nRequest:\n\n- `POST /api/tasks/{task_id}/execute`\n\nRequest body:\n\n{\n\"execution_mode\": \"api\",\n\"environment\": \"test\"\n}\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = TASK_EXECUTED`\n\n## Step 6\n\nPoll:\n\n- `GET /api/tasks/{task_id}/execution`\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = EXECUTION_OK`\n- `data.status` reaches `passed` or `failed`\n- `data.scenario_results` exists\n\n## Step 7\n\nRequest:\n\n- `GET /api/tasks/{task_id}/analysis-report`\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = ANALYSIS_REPORT_OK`\n- `data.task_id = {task_id}`\n- `data.summary` exists\n- `data.quality_status` exists\n\n## Step 8\n\nRequest:\n\n- `DELETE /api/tasks/{task_id}`\n\nExpected:\n\n- HTTP `200`\n- `code = TASK_ARCHIVED`\n- `data.task_id = {task_id}`\n- `data.archived = true`",
